title: Mo Money, Even Mo Problems
itunes:title: Mo Money, Even Mo Problems
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I’m back… after listening to all the advice you guys had, it lifted my spirits a little bit. Even J. Anthony Brown and Tommy were trying to help. But I’ve had more drama and my stress level is even higher. Steve, I thought I still had some player left in me, but no, I don’t. My wife’s niece still comes to the house to cook, but I steer clear of her. I have stayed in the basement or left the house, just to avoid her. She was there recently and I told my wife I was going jogging. When I came back, I went in through the basement because the niece was there................
